      "num": "01 · the shape",
      "heading": "Confidence is not the same as permission",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">A model can sound calm while standing on thin evidence. That is dangerous in support flows where the next sentence may affect money, health, access, or trust.</p>"
        },
