      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "Automation should lower the human cost",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">The handoff is not failure. It is how the system protects the user, the team, and the brand when the model reaches the edge of its lane.</p>"
